node.text:
.
.

For this Kingsford Grill challenge, I am tailgating at home with sliders! These shredded buffalo chicken cheese sliders are a crowd favorite! I challenge you to try these out and join the Kingsford Grill Challenge to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler! Find more recipes and techniques by visiting Kingsford.com or by going to @kingsford on Instagram. 💯
.
*Kingsford Grill Challenge*
.
Enter the Grill Challenge for a chance to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler!
.
1. Must be following @Kingsford
2. Watch the Grill Challenge, try your own at home
3. Post an image of your creation or any proud grilling moment, tag @Kingsford and make sure to use #KingsfordSweepstakes in your caption
.
Good luck! All entries must be submitted by September 20, 2021 at 11:59am EST. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, administered by or associated with Instagram, Inc. or YETI®. U.S. only.
.
Rules: http://cnvrt.us/kingsfordsweepstakes1

node.text:
.
.

For this Kingsford Grill challenge, I am tailgating at home with sliders! These shredded buffalo chicken cheese sliders are a crowd favorite! I challenge you to try these out and join the Kingsford Grill Challenge to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler! Find more recipes and techniques by visiting Kingsford.com or by going to @kingsford on Instagram. 💯
.
*Kingsford Grill Challenge*
.
Enter the Grill Challenge for a chance to win a YETI® Tundra 35 Hard Cooler!
.
1. Must be following @Kingsford
2. Watch the Grill Challenge, try your own at home
3. Post an image of your creation or any proud grilling moment, tag @Kingsford and make sure to use #KingsfordSweepstakes in your caption
.
Good luck! All entries must be submitted by September 20, 2021 at 11:59am EST. This giveaway is in no way sponsored, administered by or associated with Instagram, Inc. or YETI®. U.S. only.
.
Rules: http://cnvrt.us/kingsfordsweepstakes1
